<plot>This short, released in the US as part of the "Scotland Yard Featurettes", is the same as "The Fatal Twist" segment of the UK feature "Tale of Three Women": A phonograph record provides the clue which leads a wealthy London jeweler to the gallows and his wife and mistress to jail after he had staged a fake hold-up of his own shop.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?557752</url></doc>
